Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下に残された４５組を救うため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:13.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To save the 45s still trapped underground, Kaiji seeks a miraculous turnaround.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を増やす起死回生の方法を\N探し求めるカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある男に連れられ\N訪れた裏カジノで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:19.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An then, led to an illegal casino by a certain man, Kaiji sees it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが出会ったのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,究極のモンスターマシン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate monster machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人食い沼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man-eating Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:30.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}The Final Gamble
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:31.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出そうで出ないって…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:32.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Takes you right up to the edge without paying out. What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:35.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも あるのかよ\N誰か この台で勝ったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Has anyone ever hit the jackpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが ある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two men in the past decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:41.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この10年で２人\N２人？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この店じゃ｢達成者｣と呼んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:45.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We call them "meisters".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just two?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった２人？\Nいやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:53.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It may be just two, but they almost bled the place dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった２人でも出血大サービスだ\N店からすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:57.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この裏カジノ内にある\N他のパチンコの出玉は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In this illegal casino,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:01:02.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the other pachinko machines are computerized to pay out 50 or 70 balls per hundred put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100打って 50か70の返しに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コンピューターで\Nコントロールされている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この沼に限り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:07.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the Bog pays out 100 for each 100 bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100打てば100返し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで客が営々と\N打ち込んできた足元の玉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Under their feet lie all the balls previous gamblers had bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったー！\N当たれば それが全返し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:11.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:14.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When someone hits the jackpot, they all come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ならば５億！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, there's 500 million worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,4000円で借りた玉は\N4000円で返ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:20.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A 4000-yen ball can be sold back for 4000 yen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:24.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it really does pay back every yen that's put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:24.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,等価交換　明白な100返しだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや それ以上かもな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, maybe even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:28.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼は一度出てしまうと\N客の うまみはなくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:33.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once someone hits the jackpot on the Bog, it's far less tempting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰も勝負しなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:35.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one plays it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで３億分の玉がたまるまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:41.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So the house puts up 300 million worth of balls until the jackpot reaches that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店側が\Nその３億を請け負うシステム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉がたまっていない時点で\N当たりが出れば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:47.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If someone hits jackpot before then, the house eats the loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店は丸損　完全な持ち出し！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい よせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この手のカジノが\N収益の見込みゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:51.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This kind of casino isn't even supposed to pay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手すりゃ持ち出しなんて台を\N置いておくはずがねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:55.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't set up a machine that they could make that much of a loss on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも そう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カジノ側に必ず収益はある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There has to be something in it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えられるのは２つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can only think of two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,客に分からない程度に あの沼から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:08.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Either they're stealing balls, bit by bit, out of the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しずつ玉を抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でなければ\Nあの２人が絡んでいると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:13.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those two were plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見るべきだろうな\Nああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:19.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those are the two men who hit the Bog's jackpot this past decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが さっき言った この10年で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この沼から玉を出した２人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The meisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢達成者｣だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:25.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa! Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川　兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:30.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man on the right won a billion and a half a around a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右側の男は つい１年前に15億
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左のじいさんは５年前に30億
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the one on the left won three billion five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この２人が店側と\N通じていたと考えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:38.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If these men were working with the house, then that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話は早い\N一番 合理的な回収の方法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's probably the easiest way to make money off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど そういう話か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは偶然 出たんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに店の意思\Nつまり接待パチンコ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The house was behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They set them up to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:55.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔ども お前らが元締めか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're always behind things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと あの地獄から\Nはい上がったと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd risen from that abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何て因果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a terrible fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここも お前らの巣かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is just another of your dens of villainy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:14.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But even if it was a setup, that "Bog" machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし はっきりした
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例え それが店側の意図であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの沼とかいう台は…\Nどうだった 兄さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:19.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So, how about it? You interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か興味を引かれるようなもの\Nあったかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出る\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまく裏を突くことができりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:27.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Find the trick, and the Bog pays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの1000倍台の沼は… 出る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょー！そのとおりだよ 兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You got it, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが わしが見込んだ男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew I picked the right guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは坂崎孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm Kotaro Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた 名前は？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ… 伊藤開司だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:43.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. Kaiji Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんには\Nいろいろ話したいこともあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:58.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of things we need to talk about, Kaiji. Stay at my place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は泊っていってや
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:09.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと見てくれ\Nえ？うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっ… これ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は あのカジノに\Nわしと通じてる奴がいてな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:16.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I know a guy that works at that casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼の製造元を教えてもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:20.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He told me how the Bog works, and I made a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再現してもらったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:25.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By the time I paid him to keep his mouth shut, it cost me a few million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ口止め料を含めて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウン百万の手間賃が\Nかかったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあに ５億 ６億出れば\N全てチャラだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But compared to the five or six hundred million jackpot, that's pocket change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog doesn't cough up its jackpot easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん沼は\N普通にぶつかって出る台じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店側がそういう設定にしておる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The house has it set up not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが偶発的でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:40.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But because it's rigged to pay out when they want it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意図的に 出す 出さないが\N決まるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:44.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言えば その仕組みを\Nよくよく理解すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:46.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,if you know the trick, you can hit the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出し得るってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you want to take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる気なんだな あの沼を？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろんや
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ この作戦には共犯者が必要や
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:56.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I need an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり？\Nわしは やるべきことはやる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味は分かるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手は真っ当な やり方で出ない台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we keep it clean, it'll never pay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちたければ その逆をやること
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we wanna win, we have to do things the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:13.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 カジノ側にバレたら\Nタダじゃ済まない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:13.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And if the casino figures us out, we're fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく半殺し… わしだけでなく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:18.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll beat me half to death. And my accomplice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力者もな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに どうして俺を？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感じるんだよ 気迫を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can feel your intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の身を捨てても勝とう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:30.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your will to win no matter what, even if it means sacrificing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝たなければいけないという\N執念 意志を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well? You in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ 受けてもらえんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにリスクは高い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:38.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's risky, but the payoff is in a whole other league.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:38.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが成功したら 報酬もケタ違いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出玉の５パーセントを約束する
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll give you five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:48.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Counting the bets until we do it, I'll have 600 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから打つ客がいることも\N考えりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが打つ頃には 出玉は約６億
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:53.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その５パーセントは3000万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:51.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Five percent of that is 30 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破格の報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An incredible payout!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分自身のことだけを考えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:06:00.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,More than enough money to pay off his own debts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分すぎる金額
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし… だが しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは４５組を救えない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not enough to save the 45s!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10…\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten percent. Sixty million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出玉の10パーセント　6000万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むっ… おいおい そりゃ強欲だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dude, you're pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バレたら半殺しって言ったが\Nひょっとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're gonna beat me half to death if we get found out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:22.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit, I might never walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二度と歩けない体に\Nされるかもしれねえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10だ　この線は譲れねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten percent. Not a penny less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:33.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにな　まさか殺すまでは\Nしないだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think they'd actually kill us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暴力には弾みってもんがある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fights like that tend to get out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:39.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んじまったなんてことも\N十分 あり得る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:45.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　10パーセントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine. Ten percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまねえ\Nいやいや いいってことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,De nada, de nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're after something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:53.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 必死なんだろ　カイジくんも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら カイジくんも飲みなって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって攻略するつもりなんだ\Nあの沼を？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:00.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So how do we take down the Bog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:05.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the day we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手に話して寝返られでもしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you rat me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　そんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! I'd never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プハーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:19.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess. I know it wouldn't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むろん ないだろう\Nそんなことしても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくんに得はない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この勝負 急所は\Nギリギリまで秘めておきたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I still want to keep things secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしだけの胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep my cards close to my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It may not make much sense, but that's how I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理不尽に思うかもしれんが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも必死なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは週に４日 夜警の仕事をし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:38.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I make about 150 thou a month working for nights a week as a watchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:38.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月15万の収入で生活している
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:44.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But up until a couple years ago, I was an inspector for a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが こう見えて２年前までは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大手ゼネコンの\N現場監督をしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし長引く不況のあおりで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:49.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But he was unlucky and got laid off due to the recession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あえなくリストラの憂き目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気力を失い\Nパチンコざんまいを重ねるうち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:55.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Drowning his sorrows in pachinko, he wore out his welcome with his wife and divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妻に愛想を尽かされ 離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The old lady took my daughter when she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女房は娘を連れて出ていったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Little Mikoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美心っていってな　二十歳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,She's 20 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… ブサイクだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,She's a fucking dog. Why does she have to look so much like her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで父親に似なくても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美人な娘だろ\Nえっ ええっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't my daughter so beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美心は美人だからなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikoko, you're so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別れる時に退職金を含めた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:27.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When we split up, I sold everything, added in my savings, and gave half to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貯金やら車や家具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:24.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 一切合切を金に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女房と折半してな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから慰謝料やら何やら引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:32.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take alimony and all my other expenses out of that, and I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 わしの手元に残ったのが2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,に… 2000万？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,20 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's out warchest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが今回の軍資金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:43.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは わしが生きてきた\N人生の証しみたいな金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This money is my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってくれ カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:49.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You understand how afraid I am of losing it all, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは今 臆病なんだ 失うことに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　わしを信じて\N今は何も聞かんでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:54.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Just believe in me! Don't ask any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったよ\Nカイジくん！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当日まで何も聞かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll stay quiet until the day we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　さすがカイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks! You're a real man, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事な男っぷりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも俺には\N選択の余地なんて ねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:21.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no other way I can make 60 million in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:21.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日で6000万なんて話\N他にあるわけねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしても今 必要なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of money I need right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金が…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You pick a day yet, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっさん　勝負する日は\N決まってるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time to sit around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺 あんまり\Nのんびりしてられねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:44.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Six days from now. Tuesday the 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は６日後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10日の火曜だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 10th? Is there something special about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:47.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10日？その日に何かあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I can show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ このくらいは\N見せても いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the pin maintenance schedule for the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは例の沼の\N釘調整の予定表だ 今月のな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This month's, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘調整の予定表？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The pin maintenance schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:15.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are these A and B marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＡとかＢとかってのは？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘設定の３つのパターンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There are three pin patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釘が３パターン？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three pin patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:25.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Usually, the Bog's closed up tighter than a nun's snatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うまでもなく あの沼は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもギチギチに締めている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:29.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく役モノに落ちる\N通過ロードを通らなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:31.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not even worth playing with the jackpot blocked off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話にならないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:33.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが容易じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:38.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On B days, one of every 60 balls starts the jackpot roll. On C days, one of every hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定Ｂで60発
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｃなら100発に１つっていう難関だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 設定Ａなら30発に１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:45.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But on setting A, the pins are rigged to drop one of every 30 balls in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの道に玉が落ちるよう\N釘が調整してある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:52.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And this month, the only day with setting A is Tuesday the 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:50.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今月 その設定Ａの唯一の日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが10日の火曜日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… どうして こんな物を？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:55.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:11:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ？あのカジノに１人\N通じてる人間がいると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:11:00.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you, I know someone on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That slip of paper's worth millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ それ１枚で何百万も\Nふんだくられたがね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？何だ これ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ やば！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった？このメモの意味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いや　全然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:31.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だっ だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この坂崎に異変が起きたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:38.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something changes in Sakazaki the night before the attempt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負前日の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:59.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… おっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:07.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, Sakazaki chatters cheerfully! But today, he sits still, staring off into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普段は陽気に話し込む坂崎が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この日は座りこみ\Nただ ぼーっとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…かと思えば！\Nエヘッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It appears, but..!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？\Nウヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっ どうしたんだよ　おっさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, pops!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日 神が舞い降りた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today... God comes down from heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見捨ててなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I haven't been abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:38.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神様は わしを見捨ててなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:36.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,God hasn't abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおいおい　何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかりしてくれよ おっさん\Nおい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この坂崎の異常な言動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:48.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji only understood Sakazaki's change, his excitement,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高ぶりの意味を\Nカイジが知ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:52.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翌日 すなわち勝負当日の朝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:52.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the next morning! The day they challenge the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:59.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだよ？\N持ち金は2000万って言ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You said you had twenty mil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで5000万に増えてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How'd you end up with fifty!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:09.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you. God came down from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:10.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったろ　神が舞い降りたって\Nええっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:14.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I got the money in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間に合ったんだよ　金の工面が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか どこかの高利貸しから？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you go to some loan shark!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えてるかな\N前にチラッと見たメモ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You remember that note you looked at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひと月前 夜警の仕事中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:34.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,About a month ago, while working as a guard, I found the prez's wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,社長の財布を拾った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:42.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling I should poke through it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは ちょっとした予感があって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その財布の中を改めた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピーンときた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The combination to the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはダイヤル式金庫の番号\N中小企業の社長は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:53.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A lot of smaller companies keep the combo on paper in case the boss forgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金庫の番号を\N忘れちまった時の用心に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうにメモに控えて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:58.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They write it down and put it in their wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,財布に入れておくことが\Nあるんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:04.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A realization Sakazaki had from his life before layoffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:01.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リストラという\N人生の憂き目を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この坂崎ならではの嗅覚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一応 暗号化してあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's written in code.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Took me about half an hour to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,30分で解読できたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:14.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at where it says "ro" and "e". Those are right and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは この｢ろ｣と｢え｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは右と左を表す\N右と左？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right and left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右という漢字にはカタカナで｢ロ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you're writing in kanji, right and left are almost the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左という字には\N｢エ｣が入っとるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,except for the parts that look like "ro" and "e".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:27.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki figured out right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:26.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暗号の入り口を解明した坂崎は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ろ｣と｢え｣\Nそれぞれの横にある ひらがなを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:31.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Next, the first letters of number of times to spin the dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤルを回す回数と読み解いた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:37.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So Ro-Fo 42—Turn the dial right four times to 42!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち｢ろし-42｣は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:39.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右へ４回 回して42を合わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤルを突破したら あとは鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,After cracking the combination, all I needed was the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:48.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki spent a month searching for the key, and!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎は１ヵ月間 密かに探し続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:53.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開いたんだよ 奇跡の扉が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The door of miracles has opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく脱税したであろう金が\Nたんまり詰まっていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:57.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And all the money they were hiding from the taxman was right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ じゃあ この金は…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then this money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I took a little bit of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:03.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中から少し借りてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:07.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The more money we have going in, the better our odds are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍資金は多い方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ確率が高まるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまけに社長は出張中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:13.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, the prez is having issues anyway. He won't notice the missing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:13.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金庫を開けられる心配はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We win, I put it back, and we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って全額返せば 問題なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ちょっと待て\Nでも それって犯罪じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that illegal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ？だから？\N犯罪だからやめろって言うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're gonna back out because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？\N泥棒だからやめろって言うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A little bit of pilfering scares you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおいおい　目 覚ませ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on! Wake the fuck up! Listen to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 キレイごと言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you even trying to win!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんで本当に勝つ気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍資金が\Nあと100万 200万足りなくて負けた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:42.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You gonna be happy when we run out of money before we hit the jackpot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…なんてことになっても\Nいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then don't argue with how I get my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら手段なんて\N選んでられないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらに今 そんな余裕はない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今はまず 勝つことだ\N勝つためには 何でもやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need to win! No matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか 勝つことが前提だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Winning is everything, okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:00.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝って初めて 人生が始まるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We win, and start a new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罪も罰も知ったことか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:04.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Worry about right and wrong later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこたあ 後回し\Nそれより まず今は勝つことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:10.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, we need to win! Win, win, win! Right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:10.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ 勝つ 勝つ！違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:14.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや ちっ… 違わない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:19.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right, pops. I'm making mountains out of molehills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんの言うとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四の五のぬかして躊躇して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gonna happen if we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 負けましたじゃ\N何が何やら分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But we need...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使える金があるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ 使うわな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Every cent we can get our hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:30.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ　俺がどうかしてたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？分かりゃいい 分かりゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See? You get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, here's how it goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて 本題だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼攻略　勝ちへの策
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here's how we beat the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってたぜ この瞬間を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:52.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜 カジノには\Nまずカイジが１人で入る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:03.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji enters the casino alone that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ちょっと\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,缶ビールを１本 手にし\N坂崎の到着を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:08.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Drinking a can of beer, he waits for Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all there is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりなの それで？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またまたー\N本当はまだ何か あるんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:25.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策ってのは\N単純なくらいの方がいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:25.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The simplest plans are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純だが 誰もできんかったことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's simple, and anyone can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,度胸がなくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You just need guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:34.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,See, this is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:34.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ　これが今 言ったブツだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When I give the signal... Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが合図したら 頼むぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さりげなくな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let on that you're doing it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まんざらダメってわけでもないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:18:00.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That last tray is tuned perfectly to make sure nothing makes it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに あの最大難関の釘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶妙かつ微妙な調整で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終的には入らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなふうに仕組まれている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは その微妙な調整を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:08.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I can throw it out of whack with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつで くるわすことができれば\Nあるいは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまできたら 賭けるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんの強運 ツキに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope his luck holds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらへ どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったね 空いてて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:42.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki is checked for magnets, his person and belongings searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坂崎は厳重な磁気チェック\Nボディーチェック
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,荷物検査を通過\Nよし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:43.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:49.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして怪物 沼と対峙する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:49.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then he begins his battle with the monstrous Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:19:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,300万 500万 1000万とある\Nパッキーカードのうち
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:19:00.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's offered three-million, five-million, and ten-million yen cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Without hesitation, he goes for the ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迷わず1000万を購入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男 坂崎孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:28.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Kotaro Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,52歳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:34.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Age fifty-two! Laughing or crying, always second fiddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:34.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泣いても笑っても全財産
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日スッたら スッテンテン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's going to throw it all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の大博奕！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:41.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is my last gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,応援してくれや みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheer me on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一 出た時は祝儀を弾もう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:51.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When I hit the jackpot, we're having a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Half a mil for each of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人あたま 50万！\Nおおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:57.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,盛り上げてくれや\Nうおーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's get this started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:04.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is my last party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは わしの人生最後の祭り
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祭りだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki's challenge begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始まる　坂崎の挑戦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,究極のモンスターマシン 沼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:11.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The ultimate monster machine, the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:15.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A madman's game, at 4000 yen a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気の沙汰　１発4000円
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He aims for 600 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狙うは６億！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:38.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji S2 DVD Vol. 1 will be available for rental soon, on June 22nd!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:56.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And volume 3 of the Bog arc of Gambling Apocalypse Kaiji is on sale June 8th!
